                        <h2>Container Registry<span>Container Registry</span></h2>
                        <h4>Manage a Docker private registry as a first-class Azure resource</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_site_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
